rcusum 1.0
===========

* added an ShinyApp to interactivly perform cusum analysis

* new `cusum.obs_minus_exp` function which implements cumulative observed minus expected failure plots for unadjusted and risk adjusted analysis

* new `cusum.sprt` is the risk-adjusted sequential probability ratio test (SPRT) chart with control limits. Basically the risk-adjust counterpart of the cusum log-likelihood chart.

* new `cusum` function implemets cusum chart and cusum log-likelihood chart with control limits for performing formal hypothesis testing
